rComments: Good prof but didn't really have a goal to the class so it was just a lot of information without a clear goal or themes.
Great young prof! Prof Boyes made lectures really interesting. He's a really down to earth guy who should teach other history profs how to be interesting and teach properly.

Young prof that has a passion for history. He clearly outlines subject matter and keeps lectures interesting by playing music/video clips, recalling anecdotes and cracking jokes. He outlines what he wants and his comments on papers are very helpful.
